description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Are you a Registered Nurse looking for a new challenge?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Are you looking for a rewarding role where you can work 1:1 with a patient in their own home?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking an experienced and committed Registered Nurse to support our young service user and lead her care team in delivering the highest quality care within her home.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This lovely young girl is currently being homeschooled. She enjoys having books read to her and also likes to watch TV. Her other hobbies include listening to music, visiting the local park when the weather permits and spending time with her family.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Applicants must hold a valid NMC PIN, have experience in either children&#39;s or adults nursing and be able to evidence hands-on clinical care.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Essential Experience Required&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;*Current NMC PIN&lt;br /&gt;* Gastrostomy Care &lt;br /&gt;* Oxygen Therapy&lt;br /&gt;* Oral &amp; Nasal Suctioning&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We have the following shifts available;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;* Weekday shifts (7-hour shifts)&lt;br /&gt;* Night shifts (9-hour shifts)&lt;br /&gt;* Alternate weekend day shifts (12-hour shifts)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The role we have will enable you to make a positive impact using your valuable skills and experience.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You will also gain job satisfaction from the positive effects of your hands-on care.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Why work for Apollo Home Healthcare?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We specialise in the provision of highly complex clinical care services delivered in the homes of service users.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are passionate about delivering the highest standard of care and we recognise that our Nurses, Healthcare Assistants and Support Workers are integral to doing this. In return for your hard work and dedication you will receive:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Flexible hours to suit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Confirmed rotas&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent rates of pay&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Holiday pay&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Full clinical training&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Opportunity to work with other service users in the area&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ongoing professional training and development&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We need key workers on the front line supporting our service users in the fight against the COVID-19 Pandemic.&lt;/p&gt;
